Package gov.usgs.volcanoes.core.quakeml Description

A package to work with QuakeML 1.2 with the ANSS catalog extension.

Yes, this could probably be handled through JAXB, but that's more trouble than it's worth. QuakeML is small and stable.

See: https://quake.ethz.ch/quakeml/ https://github.com/usgs/Quakeml/wiki/ANSS-Quakeml-Catalog-Extension
